# 5WHY: On iOS static builds, QRC directory enumeration (QDir::entryList
# on qrc:/) can return empty results for directories without a qmldir.
# Explicitly declaring every QML type here eliminates the dependency on
# directory scanning and ensures all widget types resolve at QML load time.
AppIcon 1.0 AppIcon.qml
DiagnosticToolbar 1.0 DiagnosticToolbar.qml
DiagGroupPanel 1.0 DiagGroupPanel.qml
DiagResultItem 1.0 DiagResultItem.qml
LiveProgressPanel 1.0 LiveProgressPanel.qml
SummaryCards 1.0 SummaryCards.qml
TargetAnalysisPanel 1.0 TargetAnalysisPanel.qml
TargetInputPanel 1.0 TargetInputPanel.qml
